            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Deo Soli Invic<lb break="no" n="2"/>to <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Silvinius <lb n="3"/>Materninus et <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Adiutorius At<lb break="no" n="5"/>tillus et <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Vet<lb break="no" n="6"/>tinius Paternus <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>erani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> permitten<lb break="no" n="9"/>te Varonio Lup<lb break="no" n="10"/>ulo in suo
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Autopsie R. Wiegels. Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona. (B): CIMRM: Z. 7/8: Zeilenfall nicht angegeben.</p>
            </div>
